{"tid":11665,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高登   一個被時代拋棄的廢老","createTime":"2016-11-29T11:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T13:20:55.000Z","uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e10cbbed5cb1d69c350ce494079f6378cb9e62d9","tid":11665,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"高登，曾經輝煌一時，滿載大家既回憶既討論區，<br />\n今時今日，上佢website 仲睇到佢個殘舊不堪既頁面，56k般龜速既loading，仲有存在唯一作用，就係比人恥笑既官方app, 簡直係豬腸入面既一舊屎，失敗中既失敗！<br />\n係呢個人人都用手提電話上網上forum既時代，有心人幫佢寫好第三方app, 幫佢提高用戶人數，擴闊market share, 但以林早洩為首既獨裁管治，不但打壓異己，而且不思進取，毫無自我改善既念頭，終日<br />\n食老本，漠視會員權益。<br />\n今日lihkg 既出現，不是遇然，實在係高登自己作惡所產生既必然結果。<br />\n世界潮流浩浩蕩蕩，順之者昌 逆之者亡，今日係lihkg回望高登呢個殘舊既身影，唯有借用一張圖黎同佢講聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/190613_2ee1b34e91775abbfb904765be97cc84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F190613_2ee1b34e91775abbfb904765be97cc84.jpg&h=7836c2b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"278caf7041c02600381d7265e0b869eae07e3f01","tid":11665,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfafe15a7b90fc64adbcf54e0a4c1513887d1ed","tid":11665,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}